nodes.text: War of the Bounty Hunters 5 is the upcoming fifth and final issue in the canon comic book miniseries Star Wars: War of the Bounty Hunters. The issue will be written by Charles Soule, illustrated by Luke Ross, and published by Marvel Comics on October 6, 2021.
THE ULTIMATE FINALE! THE BIGGEST EVENT OF THE YEAR
CHANGES THE FACE OF THE GALAXY!
